videoSnippet.title: "Don't Cry For Me Argentina" || Capablanca vs Villegas (1914)

Jose Raul Capablanca vs Benito Higinio Villegas
"Don't Cry For Me Argentina" (game of the day Aug-19-2014)
Exhibition Game (1914), Buenos Aires ARG, Aug-19 
Queen Pawn Game: Colle System (D04)

1. d4 d5 2. Nf3 Nf6 3. e3 c6 4. Bd3 Bg4 5. c4 e6 6. Nbd2 Nbd7 7. O-O Be7 8. Qc2 Bh5 9. b3 Bg6 10. Bb2 Bd3 11. Qd3 O-O 12. Rae1 Qc7 13. e4 de4 14. Ne4 Ne4 15. Re4 Bf6 16. Qe3 c5 17. Ne5 cd4 18. Nd7 Qd7 19. Bd4 Bd4 20. Rd4 Qc7 21. Rfd1 Rfd8 22. b4 Rd4 23. Qd4 b6 24. g3 Rc8 25. Rc1 Rd8 26. Qe3 Kf8 27. c5 bc5 28. Qe4 Rd5 29. bc5 g6 30. c6 Kg7 31. a4 Rd6 32. Qe5 f6 33. Qd6 Qd6 34. c7
